{"tid":1349522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］元朗分區指揮官回應721鄉黑暴動","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:00:43.000Z","uid":3513,"like":113,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"34af7518619f8b74beaaa68d9bc8d5e0b8365f8f","tid":1349522,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"1825，元朗警署分區指揮官見記者市民，表示 :<br />\n1. 尋晚當時留有門口俾人入警署。(在場社工立即反駁)  <br />\n2. 尋晚收唔到有黑社會要攻擊市民消息。<br />\n3. 尋晚 2241 第一次接報，有市民係西鐵站被恐嚇。<br />\n2245 派出兩名巡邏警。兩名巡邏警向上級匯報增援。期間再收到報警，然後再派多4架衝鋒車。衝鋒車 2320 到達西鐵站。(距離接報已過39分鐘) <br />\n<br />\n4. 有聯絡其他警區尋求支援，後來已加派人手巡邏。<br />\n5. 未知當時在西鐵站的警察有否見到白色衫人士。<br />\n6. 未知在圍村有防暴警與白衫人士被拍攝到交流的對話內容。<br />\n7. 未能回應指今晚黑幫勢力在元朗有行動的傳聞。"},{"pid":"5dd277345a3aa37c5ca2a7bcefb250e4c8d07aca","tid":1349522,"uid":82018,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:34:42.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"6ffb2e763318aaca598768213c77adf6da40a9c5","tid":1349522,"uid":3513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5dd277345a3aa37c5ca2a7bcefb250e4c8d07aca","tid":1349522,"uid":82018,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:34:42.000Z","msg":"source?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"Tg channel 岩岩社工直播recap"},{"pid":"9ca7eca34f7e0653c5d0f8a3cb4d6d9150b5f893","tid":1349522,"uid":107060,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰今日繼續提供義載 睇下有冇巴打需要<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/doeigT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/doeigT</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e2387e54c541b2b029e5d3e738370a71a2065b","tid":1349522,"uid":3513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ca7eca34f7e0653c5d0f8a3cb4d6d9150b5f893","tid":1349522,"uid":107060,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"鄭松